<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idebecd219-3a70-11f1-9081-fe88c1712d53" identifier="/us/usc/t51/s40115"><num value="40115">§ 40115.</num><heading> Aviation weather research</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Administrator may carry out a program of collaborative research with the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration on convective weather events, with the goal of significantly improving the reliability of 2-hour to 6-hour aviation weather forecasts.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idebecd21a-3a70-11f1-9081-fe88c1712d53">(<ref href="/us/pl/111/314/s3">Pub. L. 111–314, § 3</ref>, <date date="2010-12-18">Dec. 18, 2010</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/124/3381">124 Stat. 3381</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
